overview: Wow, the big 30! We wanted to celebrate by inviting two of out shanesworld.com members to go out with a porn star. We sent Brittney Sky out with a 24 year old virgin and Calli went to Texas to meet Tex. She was in for the surprise of her life when something unexpected happened to her, you won't believe her reaction! We wanted to see where and how Nakita Denise lives in a segment called "Porn Stars at Home". As you know, when you turn 30 things get a little freaky, but it's always exciting!
title: Shane's World 30: Keepin' It Real
